19 Section 37. The director may license any organization licensed to conduct the game of
20 beano, under the provisions of section 38 to sell lottery tickets, or shares, or digital pull tab
21 tickets; provided, that such tickets are sold only on the premises of said organization for which
22 such license has been issued; and provided further, that the funds derived therefrom shall be used
23 exclusively for educational, charitable or religious purposes. The commission shall sell lottery
24 tickets to such licensed organizations and any such licensed organization reselling such tickets or
25 digital pull tab tickets shall not be subject to prosecution for setting up and promoting a lottery or
26 any other crime incidental thereto or for selling or having in its possession said lottery tickets or
27 digital pull tab tickets.
28 The commission shall sell lottery tickets or authorize the sale of or digital pull tab tickets
29 to such licensed organizations and shall determine the price at which said licensed organizations
30 shall resell said tickets, which price shall be printed on each ticket. Each licensed organization
